{"tid":152554,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"武士積克(Samurai Jack)第五季11:30PM EST(12:30PM)","createTime":"2017-03-11T20:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T10:21:06.000Z","uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac0ee3fc8b75e941e9dbd3484df395690f69ea0","tid":152554,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2us.denofgeek.com/sites/denofgeekus/files/styles/article_width/public/2016/06/new-samurai-jack-promo.jpg?itok=M1MB_miK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2us.denofgeek.com%2Fsites%2Fdenofgeekus%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_width%2Fpublic%2F2016%2F06%2Fnew-samurai-jack-promo.jpg%3Fitok%3DM1MB_miK&h=33baf978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《武士積克》是美國動畫片，由格恩迪&middot;塔塔科夫斯基擔任製作，也就是《德克斯特的實驗室》的製作人。傑克武士與其他動畫不同的是，他卡通裏的任何事物皆沒有輪廓，並採用簡約的藝術風格，以及類似浮世繪的繪畫方式。傑克武士從2001年8月10日至2004年9月25日，得到了艾美獎提名6次並得獎4次，以卡通來說，提名6次得獎4次已經是成就非凡。截至第4季一共52集，格恩迪&middot;塔塔科夫斯基曾說過要出武士積克電影版，以真正結束《武士積克》。直到2016年，以成人觀眾作目標的Adult Swim宣佈傑克武士將會在此頻道重啟，這代表着從第五季起故事將會更黑暗和血腥。<br />\n11:30PM EST(12:30PM)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.adultswim.com/videos/samurai-jack/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adultswim.com%2Fvideos%2Fsamurai-jack%2F&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=84dc683d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.adultswim.com/videos/samurai-jack/</a><br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=VSrv_n4tw7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVSrv_n4tw7w&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5015dcfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=VSrv_n4tw7w</a>"},{"pid":"9b016dcf6ba1533ee6d34230746fdf646b52a03b","tid":152554,"uid":29996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T21:31:55.000Z","msg":"呢度無人睇的<br />\n<br />\n細個得閑見cartoon network播就會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de8a9720de7ad0794d86cad27ab